com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.core.model.implementation.instance
Class ModelInstance

java.lang.Object
  com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.core.model.implementation.instance.ModelInstance
Direct Known Subclasses:
ModelArrayInstance
public class ModelInstance
extends java.lang.Object

Instances of this class represent concrete Java objects on the heap. Such instances are necessarily unique (as they would be in Java) and contain information about the state of the object. Importantly, it stores the concrete values of any fields its class may have, as well as information about the ModelVariable instances referring to it.

Author:
christopher
